{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Deforb is a roguelite top-down shooter game where a mad orb  defending its tower from endless waves of enemies. Armed with up to 4 melee guns and a long-range gun, the orb uses a combination of close and ranged combat to keep the foes at bay. In addition to powerful weapons, the orb can deploy turrets, strategically placing them to help turn the tide of battle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3539060/extras/giphy__1_.gif?t=1739959025\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As the game progresses, you can upgrade your skills, choosing from a wide range of abilities that enhance your combat effectiveness and defense strategies. The key to survival lies in creating the perfect build, utilizing these upgrades to adapt to the increasingly difficult waves of enemies. Every decision you make \u2014 from weapon choice to skill upgrades \u2014 will shape your strategy, allowing you to experiment and find the most powerful combinations to protect the tower.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Demo Description:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this demo, you'll play through the first nine levels of the game, facing a selection of enemies and trying out some of the available equipment. But this is just a glimpse\u2014there are even more challenges and foes waiting for you in the full game!</p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3539060?t=1739959025","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3539060?t=1739959025","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3539060/ca579c4d95cf8f4bc09c6b0e6ff76aa358c1fb02/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739959025","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3539060/ca579c4d95cf8f4bc09c6b0e